strata1.common.money
Class MoneyCalculator

java.lang.Object
  strata1.common.money.MoneyCalculator

public class MoneyCalculator
extends Object

Provides functionality for doing arithmetic operations on Money objects. Uses CurrencyExchanger to convert Money of different currencies prior to calculations.

Author:
Sapientia Systems
